        <h3><u>Why Registration ?</u></h3><br />
        <pre>
Green Gas Limited (Joint Venture of GAIL (India) Ltd. & Indian Oil 
Corporation Limited) intends to register vendors in order to
develop a comprehensive data base of vendors for procurement of quality 
Goods /Consultancy Services/Works including Works Contracts,
Annual Maintenance/Rate Contracts leading to value for money.
The registration process is an online process, where in vendors
are required to fill requisite fields and submit the application.
Selective documents are required to be submitted at this stage.

<b>2.   Who can register?</b>

<b>a)</b> Companies/Firms/Agencies/ Cooperatives/Institutes etc. currently
     incorporated or established / registered as per relevant laws.
<b>b)</b> Sole proprietors/Independent Contractors/Consultants (Persons
     engaged in a business as either a “Self employed Individual” or as a
    “Sole Proprietor” or who is the only owner of the unincorporated trade
     or business).
<b>c)</b> Companies/Firms currently doing business with Green Gas Limited,
     are also required to register quoting their order nos. etc.
<b>d)</b> Green Gas Limited, prefers to procure products which are energy 
    efficient and conforming to National (BIS) / Indian and / or 
International standards.

<b >3.   Benefits to vendors :</b>

<b>a)</b> Get email alerts regarding NIT’s /Corrigendum in the preferred 
   category / sub-category and region.
<b>b)</b> Be able to down load soft copies of tender document from GGL’s web site.
<b>c)</b> Be able to update time related data.
<b>d)</b> Get e-mail alert for advertisement regarding empanelment and other issues.
 </pre>

